Package: wizardR
Type: Package
Title: A Package in R to generate assessment documents from a list of questions using randomization methods.
Version: 1.0.0
Author: João Caldeira
Maintainer: João Caldeira <jcppc@iscte-iul.pt>
Description: - This package, reads an excel spreadsheet with questions and answers and produce a professional assessment document with randomized questions.
    - It also generates the solutions document
    - Produce branded documents
    - Render the data into pdf documents
Depends: R (>= 4.2.2)
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: readxl
Remotes: nirmalpatel/fuzzymineR
